{"about_the_game":"The Startling Developments Detective Agency springs into action as <strong>On the Rain-Slick Precipice of Darkness 3</strong> begins, set in motion by a call from a mysterious source. The ever escalating perils on the Rain-Slick Precipice of Darkness will season our tender heroes to their very core! Expect cunning evil doctors, a series of unexplainable thefts, a mysterious book of power, enigmatic supernatural forces, hoboids, roboids, time travelling dinosaurs, and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Old-School RPG style mixed with modern design sensibilities!<br></li><li>Bizarre and humorous story written by Penny Arcade &amp; Zeboyd Games!<br></li><li>View the town of New Arcadia in all its pure, 16-bit glory!<br></li><li>8-12 hour quest with even more content to be added later via free updates!<br></li><li>No random battles!<br></li><li>Gain the powers of the Tube Samurai, the Hobo, the Apocalypt, the Dinosorcerer, the Delusionist, and more through a unique multi-class job system!<br></li><li>Disrupt enemy attacks with powerful interrupt abilities!<br></li><li>Rechargable MP &amp; items! Unleash your full power in every battle!<br></li><li>Leverage &quot;Help-Yu,&quot; our haiku-based help system. An Industry first!<br></li><li>No previous experience with Rain-Slick 1 or 2 necessary!</li></ul>","achievements":{"total":0},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/213030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1682942622","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/213030/page.bg.jpg?t=1682942622","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/213030/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1682942622","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/213030/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1682942622","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"